  <entry>
    <title>markdown语法</title>
    <link href="http://uerlink.github.io/2022/05/08/%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%8C%BA/markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <id>http://uerlink.github.io/2022/05/08/%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%8C%BA/markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</id>
    <published>2022-05-07T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-05-08T03:14:26.481Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="标题语法"><a href="#标题语法" class="headerlink" title="标题语法"></a>标题语法</h2><h1 id="一级标题"><a href="#一级标题" class="headerlink" title="一级标题"></a>一级标题</h1><h2 id="二级标题"><a href="#二级标题" class="headerlink" title="二级标题"></a>二级标题</h2><h3 id="三级标题"><a href="#三级标题" class="headerlink" title="三级标题"></a>三级标题</h3><h4 id="四级标题"><a href="#四级标题" class="headerlink" title="四级标题"></a>四级标题</h4><h5 id="五级标题"><a href="#五级标题" class="headerlink" title="五级标题"></a>五级标题</h5><h6 id="六级标题"><a href="#六级标题" class="headerlink" title="六级标题"></a>六级标题</h6><pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 三级标题.</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">另一种写法:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">===</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre><h2 id="段落语法"><a href="#段落语法" class="headerlink" title="段落语法"></a>段落语法</h2><p>空一行是换行<br>空两行是换段</p><p>注意换端的时候不要用空格或制表符</p><h2 id="强调语法"><a href="#强调语法" class="headerlink" title="强调语法"></a>强调语法</h2><p><strong>加粗</strong></p><pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="strong">**文字**</span></span><br></pre><p><em>斜体</em></p><pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*文字*</span></span><br></pre><h2 id="引用语法"><a href="#引用语法" class="headerlink" title="引用语法"></a>引用语法</h2><blockquote><p>引用文字…</p></blockquote><pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 引用文字</span></span><br></pre><blockquote><p>123456</p><blockquote><p>嵌套引用<br>12334</p></blockquote></blockquote><pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 123456</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; 嵌套引用</span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 123456</span></span><br></pre><blockquote><p>引用里面加列表</p><ul><li>1</li><li>2</li><li>3</li></ul></blockquote><pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 引用里面加列表</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; - 1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; - 2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; - 3</span></span><br></pre><h2 id="列表语法"><a href="#列表语法" class="headerlink" title="列表语法"></a>列表语法</h2><p>有序列表</p><ol><li>1</li><li>2</li><li>3<pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3.</span> 3</span><br></pre></li></ol><p>无序列表</p><ul><li>1</li><li>2</li><li>3<pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 3</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 3</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 3</span><br></pre></li></ul><p>相互嵌套</p><ol><li>1<ul><li>2</li><li>3</li></ul></li><li>4<pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 4</span><br></pre></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
